data.description: Lovely, spacious townhome in Bartram offering a private atrium. Lots of natural light fills this unit which offers three bedrooms, two and one half bathrooms. Enjoy a spacious entry leading to the kitchen and family room. Enjoy your updated kitchen with plenty of storage, lovely appliances and solid surface counter tops. Kitchen is open to the cozy family room. Tall ceilings throughout and makes the unit feel very spacious. Primary bedroom offers a large en suite, dual vanity, soaking tub and stand up shower.Great size additional bedrooms, and laundry room. Just Minutes to the Bartram Amenities, Durbin Pavilion, highways and more!
